<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She is the Mummy Diaries star known for her sense of style.</p>

<p>And Sam Faiers looked chic as she stepped out for lunch at Hakkasan, Mayfair in London on Monday.</p>

<p>The reality star, 29, wowed as she donned a cream sweater paired with a structured blazer for her outing.</p>

<p>Style: Sam Faiers looked chic as she stepped out for lunch at Hakkasan, Mayfair in London on Monday</p>

<p>Sam teamed  this with straight-leg jeans and vertiginous white heeled boots.</p>

<p>Her caramel tresses were styled in soft waves while her pretty features were enhanced with a radiant palette of make-up.</p>

<p>She slipped on some trendy shades to complete the look.  </p>

<p>Sam's outing comes after admitted she 'didn't want to leave the house' during her two-year struggle with cystic acne.</p>

<p>Style: The reality star, 29, wowed as she donned a cream sweater paired with a structured blazer for her outing</p>

<p>The former TOWIE startold OK! her confidence took a huge hit after her acne flared up when she began breastfeeding her daughter Rosie, but she's finally got her skin under control with the help of collagen supplements.</p>

<p>Sam only revealed her battles with acne last month after weeks of hiding her flare-ups with heavy makeup and filters..  </p>

<p>She told the magazine: 'I never wanted to leave the house. I had to put on thick foundation and when I was posing I was like ''I don't want to show this side of my face.'' </p>

<p>Looking good: She slipped on some trendy shades to complete the look</p>

<p>Difficult: Sam's outing comes after admitted she 'didn't want to leave the house' during her two-year struggle with cystic acne</p>

<p>'Some days I didn't even want to go out. When I was talking to people I thought they were all looking at my skin.</p>

<p>Sam added that she's overcome her skin struggles with the help of collagen supplements and she's finally comfortable with her complexion ahead of her 30th birthday later this year.  </p>

<p>She added: 'You know what, my skin to me is now perfect. I don't have to slap on the foundation. I've tried everything but I've finally found what works for me.'</p>

<p>Last month Sam spoke about her struggles with cystic acne for the first time as she took to Instagram to share a snap of her bad flare-up.</p>

